{"tid":1650103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"煩緊眼罩嘅手足同我入黎","createTime":"2019-10-12T20:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T13:11:25.000Z","uid":273185,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"58dad80ebfbff37cbe62501da52f7721e2c34855","tid":1650103,"uid":273185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T20:51:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">見到依家仲有好多手足仲用緊泳鏡<br />\n因為氣密眼罩難入手,又未必啱面型,價錢仲要偏高,萬一要棄裝就好肉赤。相反泳鏡易入手,一定啱面型,價錢就有高有低,但勝在唔洗棄</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但係小弟我自己都有用過泳鏡,戴住之後視野會有都幾多嘅限制,仲要勁唔舒服 戴耐咗真係勁想除</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">於是我參考咗之前一啲手足嘅方法,整咗個整合版嘅出黎</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">就係普通眼罩+電線膠紙+3M海綿膠條</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BoqJUoe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBoqJUoe.png&h=6e93a1a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jhjnqvQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjhjnqvQ.png&h=e1407eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mf80caV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmf80caV.png&h=65dc9d04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">之前都有聽過同睇過有手足教過類似方法,但係又好似唔普遍</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">製作成本非常之低,呢到總成本都係60蚊有找</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">眼罩$1X-2X<br />\n電線膠紙$X<br />\n3M海綿膠條$3X-4X</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其中電線膠紙同膠條都好大卷,可以整到10副左右.成本效益都可以話係唔錯</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">其次佢地嘅入手程度亦都相當容易,眼罩只係最普遍嘅1621,大部分五金鋪都好大機會會有,而電線膠紙亦都係五金鋪搵到,去到問佢有無黑色電線膠紙就得,但係你想要其他色都可以嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而最後嘅海綿膠條可以係日本城到搵到.可以話係邊到都可以買齊到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">當然到最後,亦最關心嘅一定係你講咁耐到底做唔做到氣密</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我測試過係<span style=\"color: red;\">完全唔入水</span>,就算你見我鼻位痴得咁樣衰都無事,黎緊打war game就會去試下,麻煩各位巴絲打唔好相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位手足如果覺得ok就麻煩幫手推下,P牌仔推唔到</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">PS:戴眼鏡會令則邊有罅</span></span>"},{"pid":"95d7cb15547509343284251596bf591ba4bb6b18","tid":1650103,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T20:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa01ab7fda24333025bfa24f255822ca2f0f442","tid":1650103,"uid":158504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T21:03:52.000Z","msg":"呢啲時間未必推得上<br />\n建議copy入裝備post推下"},{"pid":"312eb8ab823ae1c0a719316ec2336940b02144f9","tid":1650103,"uid":261530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T21:04:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"701261b099652c88d63b13ab1f2788e839796631","tid":1650103,"uid":261530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T21:05:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff95c7368a69b42bf3f13c206100338950dce667","tid":1650103,"uid":261530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T21:05:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cba5e56e91b20dd7662593dfb07e9e55aee2c0a","tid":1650103,"uid":261530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T21:05:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a06becd29b1ed5bb39afe874059ef3ccbd0c4d8","tid":1650103,"uid":111658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T21:06:20.000Z","msg":"海綿貼得唔好 好容易入氣"},{"pid":"60b1590e13b427c23aeacf9f71f4714ef49b7c34","tid":1650103,"uid":273185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfa01ab7fda24333025bfa24f255822ca2f0f442","tid":1650103,"uid":158504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T21:03:52.000Z","msg":"呢啲時間未必推得上<br />\n建議copy入裝備post推下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T07:00:16.000Z","msg":"裝備post姐係咩台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a182da51d994b10ce85f09bb9ae751d91e380c89","tid":1650103,"uid":273185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a06becd29b1ed5bb39afe874059ef3ccbd0c4d8","tid":1650103,"uid":111658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T21:06:20.000Z","msg":"海綿貼得唔好 好容易入氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"呢個我真係答你唔到住,今日先試到 但係至少我試詔係唔入水卮"},{"pid":"c41fb35b47a3ace43914b4f237e3d059b013f3fc","tid":1650103,"uid":16520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:11:25.000Z","msg":"可以用高密度氣密條（都係3M；眼鏡位剪一刀，最好戴幼眶眼鏡），然後再痴你圖入面嗰款氣密條。"}]}